  <section>
    <title>Overview</title>

    <para>The purpose of an array is to store multiple parameters under one
    object, such as components of a vector.</para>

    <section>
      <title>Listing of Objects and Commands that interact</title>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Report Command</para>

          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>Report commands can be used to retrieve information within
              arrays or from the entire array.</para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>
  </section>

